International Sales Executive
29 Apr 2014 09:44 PM - UAE
My client is a UK based property investment and asset management firm. They are opening an office in Dubai to sell UK property to high net-worth Middle East investors. They are looking for experienced agents to join their team to manage a huge portfolio of clients in Saudi Arabia & the UAE.They are offering an excellent basic salary with a high commission structure.Please send your CV if you are:• Arabic Speaking• At least 2 years in Real Estate, in the UAE or UK• Live in Dubai• (more...)
